OL,3,CGordon Smart reports on why many
OL,4,Cadults in the UK are facing a stress
OL,5,Cepidemic
OL,7,FEarlier this year the charity Mental
OL,8,FHealth UK released a report which
OL,9,Ffound that Britain is now at risk of
OL,10,Fbecoming a burnt out nation, with nine
OL,11,Fout of ten people living with either
OL,12,Fhigh or extreme levels of stress.
OL,14,FIn this episode of ITV's Tonight
OL,15,Fprogramme, Gordon Smart finds out more
OL,16,Fabout modern day stress and explores
OL,17,Fwhether we can beat it.
