OL,3,CGordon Smart reports on why many
OL,4,Cadults in the UK are facing a stress
OL,5,Cepidemic
OL,7,FWe meet Ngozi Weller who shares her
OL,8,Fpersonal experience of reaching
OL,9,Fburnout eight years ago whilst working
OL,10,Fin a high pressure job in an oil and
OL,11,Fgas industry. Stress affected her
OL,12,Fmentally and physically, and she was
OL,13,Fsigned off work by her GP. With time
OL,14,Fand support she recovered, but she
OL,15,Fdidn't return to her original career.
OL,16,FInstead she founded her own business
OL,17,Fworking with companies to tackle the
OL,18,Fissue of stress in the workplace.
