OL,3,CGordon Smart reports on why many
OL,4,Cadults in the UK are facing a stress
OL,5,Cepidemic
OL,7,FGordon meets former Royal Marine Sam
OL,8,FMurray, whose life was revolutionised
OL,9,Fby discovering breathwork and ice
OL,10,Fbaths. Sam underwent professional
OL,11,Ftraining and started a company with
OL,12,Fhis partner Miranda who is a
OL,13,Fbreathwork practitioner. They now
OL,14,Fspend their days running workshops for
OL,15,Fthe public, and working closely with
OL,16,Fthe emergency services, NHS workers
OL,17,Fand military veterans.
