OL,7,FIt's important to note that ice baths
OL,8,Fare not suitable for everyone, and can
OL,9,Fbe dangerous if not done correctly. It
OL,10,Fis important to receive medical advice
OL,11,Ffirst, and only go ahead in a
OL,12,Fcontrolled environment, under expert
OL,13,Fsupervision.
OL,15,FTo find out more about modern day
OL,16,Fstress, and how we can tackle it,
OL,17,FTonight devised an experiment, with
OL,18,FPhysiologist Oliver Patrick.
