OL,3,CGordon Smart reports on why many
OL,4,Cadults in the UK are facing a stress
OL,5,Cepidemic
OL,7,FWe followed two people with
OL,8,Fnotoriously stressful jobs: Chef Zak
OL,9,Ffrom Manchester, and teacher Hannah
OL,10,Ffrom Essex. Our test tracked their
OL,11,Fheart rate variability and revealed
OL,12,Fthat both were having difficulty
OL,13,Fswitching off and giving their bodies
OL,14,Ftime to recover from stress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
