OL,3,CGordon Smart reports on why many
OL,4,Cadults in the UK are facing a stress
OL,5,Cepidemic
OL,7,FThey then tried some stress busting
OL,8,Ftechniques including mindful eating,
OL,9,Fgetting out into nature, practising
OL,10,Fyoga, and listening to audiobooks
OL,11,Fduring their commute. The data showed
OL,12,Fthat building more 'recovery' time
OL,13,Finto their daily routine with these
OL,14,Fsorts of activities had a positive
OL,15,Fimpact on their heart variability and
OL,16,Foverall stress levels.
